### 🧩 Add Your Source Files

Now put all your `.cpp` files (the ones we wrote together) into the same folder:

- `SequencePlayer.cpp`
- `EmojiPlayer.cpp`
- `ImagePlayer.cpp`

(You can also include `ChasingRomeo.cpp` if you have it.)

---

### 🚀 Push to GitHub

```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial release"
git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo-name.git
git push -u origin main
